Bulding bsod-client.

Install:
 * libsdl-devel
 * zlib-devel

Make sure OpenGL of some sort is also installed, you may need to install
Mesa if the build fails to find OpenGL or GLU. You'll also need Python
installed.

Build DevIL and lua:
 * DevIL:
    cd external/DevIL
    ./configure --prefix=`pwd`/.. --enable-static=yes
    make clean install
    cd ../..
 * lua:
    cd external/lua
    make
    cd ../..

Build bsod-client:
 * make

Configure bsod-client:
 * vi data/config.lua

Run:
 * ./bsod-client
